query:
PREFIX ns3: <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>

SELECT (COUNT(?sensorSwitch) AS ?sensorSwitchCount) 
WHERE {
  ?sensorSwitch rdf:type ns3:HardwareShape .
  ?sensorSwitch ns3:hasCategory ?category .
  ?category ns3:categoryName "Sensor Switch" .
}

How many suppliers do we have in France?
query:
PREFIX ns3: <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>

SELECT (COUNT(DISTINCT ?supplier) AS ?supplierCount)
WHERE {
  ?supplier rdf:type ns3:SupplierShape .
  ?supplier ns3:country "France" .
}
